<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="caution-n">caution <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɔːʃn/    美 /'kɔːʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 谨慎；小心：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>with great caution</strong> 
极为小心地</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Caution is the parent of safety.
小心驶得万年船。</p></div>

<h4 id="2c-u">2.<strong>[C] &amp; [U] 警告；告诫：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>give sb a caution
告诫某人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Just a  <strong>word of caution</strong>— these glasses are very delicate so handle them with care.
提醒一句，这些玻璃杯很容易打碎，所以要小心放置。</p></div></div>